{"tid":1395534,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)Prison Break逃","createTime":"2019-08-01T19:04:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T23:02:19.000Z","uid":29160,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f234387f569fe0cac5cd8fccbd2d79bb7d7cd7a6","tid":1395534,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:04:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=c9f786c6\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=5fc8cb5f\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=32f3d0c2\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/48/Prisonbreak.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F48%2FPrisonbreak.jpg&h=10bfd496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n故事敘述主角的哥哥林肯&middot;布魯斯（Lincoln Burrows）被誣陷殺害副總統之弟，被判處死刑並將於不久後執行。麥可&middot;史考菲（Michael Scofield）得知其兄的冤情後，秘密策劃了一套詳盡可行的計劃，欲幫助林肯出獄。誰知道一連串陰謀不斷發生在他們及其身邊的人的身上<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=2c26cbca\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=oOhF4K9gmG%2F73F8T9h6VFKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=9a1fb177\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d737f17b9823b029f33b03ad2479fee049e6f9a3","tid":1395534,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T19:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f3adc22eec67821b833c0b99c05cdb9061c2c1","tid":1395534,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T20:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29fa9b6c38690bdcb7bdc71ae92df4191c157eb7","tid":1395534,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T21:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f093ad31be5404a1d7ce9a5b870b518682afed8","tid":1395534,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit